column7: The December 1, 1832 birthdate is an approximation. In the summer of 1858, Schooner's grandfather, Gurden Ockrey, declared that Schooner would be "be twenty-six years old next November or December." Ockrey also stated that Schooner had "some appearance of Indian which he gets from his Father who was a half Indian."
